Class LoggingIndexedIdGeneratorMonitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.internal.id.indexed.LoggingIndexedIdGeneratorMonitor

    public class LoggingIndexedIdGeneratorMonitor
extends Object
implements IndexedIdGenerator.Monitor, Closeable
